ROLLUP & CUBE :- 
----------------------------

  => functions used to display subtotals and grand total

                 GROUP BY ROLLUP(col1,col2,--)
                 GROUP BY CUBE(col1,col2,------)
 
ROLLUP :-
---------------
 
=> ROLLUP displays subtotals for each group  and also display grand total 

   SELECT deptno,job,SUM(sal)
   FROM emp
   GROUP BY ROLLUP(deptno,job)
   ORDER BY deptno ASC ; 
  
      10	CLERK           	1300
           	MANAGER         	2450
          	 PRESIDENT      	 5000
                          		 8750   => dept subtotal


        20	 ANALYST       	  6000
           	CLERK          	 1900
          	 MANAGER         	  2975
                          		  10875   => dept subtotal


        30 	CLERK          	  950
          	 MANAGER         	 2850
          	 SALESMAN       	 5600
                          		 9400   => dept subtotal

                          		29025   => grand total

CUBE :-
--------------

=> CUBE displays subtotals for each group by column (deptno,job)  
      and also displays grand total.

   SELECT deptno,job,SUM(sal)
   FROM emp
   GROUP BY CUBE(deptno,job)
   ORDER BY deptno ASC ; 
 
